Angular module - there is not parent child mopdule all modules merger at compile
for lazy loaded modules it needed to be declare in NGMOdule then only webpack will able to load it later

COmpinent have parent child relationship

for each component angular create Change detector which match old value and new valur of p[roperty of that component\
based on parent child relation ship between component it creates chaneg decetction tree kind of structure and from start with root it goes to bottom
to test changes.

